title: DDFP 247: 2014 NFL Draft analysis & Cardinals Darnell Dockett
itunes:title: DDFP 247: 2014 NFL Draft analysis & Cardinals Darnell Dockett
description:
Shek is joined in Studio 66 by NFL Media draft expert Bucky Brooks to break down the high-end and low-end potential for Johnny Manziel and other top prospects and to discuss where Russell Wilson and Julio Jones would rank in this draft. Arizona Cardinals star Darnell Dockett then calls in from DC to discuss the 2014 Cardinals, the rugged NFC West, and Bruce Arians' Kangol collection.
